s%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20wine%20%26quot%3Bjust%20got%20claimed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fplatform.twitter.com%2Fwidgets.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EOur%20ongoing%20experiment%20into%20whether%20anyone%20reads%20website%20T%26amp%3BCs%20continues.%20We%20put%20this%20in%20our%20terms%20back%20in%20February.%20Just%20got%20claimed.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FN7k3weTuA9%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FN7k3weTuA9%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20Dan%20Neidle%20(%40DanNeidle)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FDanNeidle%2Fstatus%2F1788483147425853899%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMay%209%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3ENeidle%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc84z2jqpvpko%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%20the%20BBC%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20T%26amp%3BCs%20stunt%20was%20%26quot%3Bmy%20childish%20protest%20that%20all%20businesses%20have%20to%20have%20a%20privacy%20policy%20and%20no-one%20reads%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20website's%20privacy%20policy%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftaxpolicy.org.uk%2Flegal%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehas%20since%20been%20updated%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20say%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20know%20nobody%20reads%20this.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmusingly%2C%20the%20person%20who%20claimed%20the%20bottle%20was%20only%20reading%20it%20because%20they%20were%20writing%20their%20own%20T%26amp%3BCs%20and%20needed%20examples%20to%20follow%2C%20Neidle%20told%20the%20BBC.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20wine%20he%20sent%20out%2C%20per%20the%20BBC%2C%20was%20a%202013-2014%20bottle%20of%20Ch%C3%A2teau%20de%20Sales%2C%20which%20retails%20for%20about%20%2444.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo-called%20%26quot%3Bgotcha%20clauses%26quot%3B%20have%20been%20around%20for%20a%20while%2C%20highlighting%20a%20seemingly%20intractable%20problem%20in%20digital%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202014%2C%20a%20security%20firm%20added%20what%20it%20called%20a%20%26quot%3BHerod%20clause%26quot%3B%20into%20a%20public%20wi-fi%20network's%20terms%20and%20conditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESix%20people%20signed%20up%20to%20%26quot%3Bassign%20their%20first%20born%20child%20to%20us%20for%20the%20duration%20of%20eternity%2C%26quot%3B%20in%20order%20to%20access%20the%20wi-fi%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Ftechnology%2F2014%2Fsep%2F29%2Flondoners-wi-fi-security-herod-clause%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eas%20The%20Guardian%20reported%20at%20the%20time%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20authors%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tandfonline.com%2Fdoi%2Ffull%2F10.1080%2F1369118X.2018.1486870%3FneedAccess%3Dtrue%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eone%202017%20study%3C%2Fa%3E%20found%20that%2098%25%20of%20participants%20signed%20up%20to%20similarly%20onerous%20terms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENeidle%20said%20he%20was%20inspired%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvan-halen-brown-m-ms-contract-2016-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20legendary%20clause%20that%20Van%20Halen%20buried%20in%20their%20tour%20rider%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20according%20to%20the%20BBC.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20each%20stop%2C%20the%20group%20demanded%20a%20bowl%20of%20M%26amp%3BMs%20with%20all%20the%20brown%20ones%20taken%20out%20%E2%80%94%20not%20because%20they%20were%20pampered%2C%20but%20because%20it%20would%20prove%20that%20the%20host%20venue%20was%20paying%20attention%20to%20more%20crucial%20safety%20and%20technical%20aspects%20of%20their%20show.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20a%20brilliant%20strategy%20to%20see%20if%20people%20were%20paying%20attention%2C%26quot%3B%20Neidle%20told%20the%20BBC.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20many%20reasons%20why%20few%20people%2