0010145.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20World%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fbusiness%2Finternational-business%2Ffrom-crypto-king-to-prison-inmate-inside-details-of-sam-bankman-frieds-jail-life%2Farticleshow%2F110010145.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fbusiness%2Finternational-business%2Ffrom-crypto-king-to-prison-inmate-inside-details-of-sam-bankman-frieds-jail-life%2Famp_articleshow%2F110010145.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fbusiness%2Finternational-business%2Ffrom-crypto-king-to-prison-inmate-inside-details-of-sam-bankman-frieds-jail-life%2Famp_articleshow%2F110010145.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BCan%20Create%20Anarchic%20Situation%26quot%3B%3A%20Poll%20Panel%20To%20M%20Kharge%20On%20Voter%20Turnout%20Data%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EReacting%20strongly%20to%20Mallikarjun's%20Kharge's%20letter%20to%20INDIA%20allies%20alleging%20discrepancies%20in%20voter%20turnout%20data%20and%20stating%20that%20the%20credibility%20of%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20is%20at%20%26quot%3Ban%20all-time%20low%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20poll%20panel%20has%20accused%20the%20Congress%20president%20of%20making%20baseless%20allegations%20to%20%26quot%3Bcreate%20confusion%2C%20misdirection%20and%20impediments%20in%20the%20conduct%20of%20free%20and%20fair%20polls%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20sharply%20worded%20and%20unprecedented%20response%20issued%20on%20Friday%2C%20the%20Election%20Commission%20said%20that%20Mr%20Kharge's%20letter%20was%20in%20the%20form%20of%20internal%20correspondence%20within%20a%20political%20grouping%20and%2C%20yet%2C%20he%20had%20made%20it%20public%20-%20a%20reference%20to%20the%20Congress%20president%20posting%20it%20on%20X.%20Condemning%20his%20question%3A%20%26quot%3BCould%20this%20be%20an%20attempt%20to%20doctor%20the%20final%20results%3F%26quot%3B%20the%20panel%20said%20it%20could%20create%20an%20anarchic%20situation%2C%20besides%20doubts%20and%20disharmony.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20the%20allegations%20levelled%20by%20Mr%20Kharge%2C%20who%20is%20also%20the%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20point%20by%20point%2C%20the%20EC%20called%20them%20%26quot%3Binsinuations%20and%20innuendos%26quot%3B%20and%20an%20%26quot%3Baggression%20on%20vitals%20of%20live%20election%20operations%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20key%20claims%20in%20Mr%20Kharge's%20letter%20-%20that%20the%20voter%20turnout%20increased%20by%20around%205.5%25%20in%20the%20first%20phase%20and%20about%205.74%25%20in%20the%20second%20phase%20and%20that%20the%20date%20was%20delayed%20-%20the%20EC%20said%20there%20was%20no%20delay%20and%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20updated%20turnout%20data%20has%20always%20been%20higher%20than%20what%20was%20released%20on%20polling%20day.%20The%20commission%20backed%20up%20this%20claim%20by%20releasing%20a%20%26quot%3Bfactual%20matrix%26quot%3B%20of%20data%20from%20elections%2C%20beginning%20with%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20very%20premise%20that%20voter%20turnout%20data%20was%20released%20late%20is%20devoid%20of%20facts%20as%20it%20has%20always%20been%20available%20on%20the%20Voter%20turnout%20APP.%20Commission%20has%20not%20changed%20the%20design%20or%20periodicity%20of%20displaying%20voter%20turnout%20data%20in%20any%20manner.%20Needless%20to%20add%20that%20polling%20station%20wise%20data%20of%20electors%20and%20voters%20is%20given%20to%20agent%20of%20the%20candidate%20on%20the%20day%20of%20poll%20itself%20at%20close%20of%20poll%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20EC%20wrote.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Transparent%20Process'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20Congress%20president's%20other%20charge%20that%20some%20media%20reports%20had%20claimed%20that%20the%20final%20registered%20voters%20list%20for%20the%20next%20phases%20had%20not%20been%20made%20public%2C%20the%20panel%20said%20that%20he%20would%20know%2C%20%26quot%3Bas%20a%20senior%20parliamentarian%2C%20a%20very%20seasoned%20politician...%20and%20as%20the%20head%20of%20a%20prominent%20National%20Political%20Party%26quot%3B%20%C2%A0that%20the%20EC%20follows%20a%20transparent%20process%20of%20preparation%20of%20electoral%20rolls.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%2C%20it%20said%2C%20is%20made%20stronger%20by%20the%20participation%20of%20political%20parties%20and%20candidates%20at%20every%20stage%20of%20the%20process%2C%20ensuring%20that%20parties%20know%20the%20number%20of%20electors%20at%20every%20stage%20of%20the%20electoral%20cycle.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715337840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fupn3k29g_m-kharge-1200-_625x300_29_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcan-create-anarchic-situation-poll-panel-to-m-kharge-on-voter-turnout-data-5632242%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Reacting%20strongly%20to%20Mallikarjun's%20Kharge's%20letter%20to%20INDIA%20allies%20alleging%20discrepancies%20in%20voter%20turnout%20data%2C%20the%20poll%20panel%20has%20accused%20the%20Congress%20president%20of%20making%20baseless%20allegations.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcan-create-anarchic-situation-poll-panel-to-m-kharge-on-voter-turnout-data-5632242%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcan-create-anarchic-situation-poll-panel-to-m-kharge-on-voter-turnout-data-5632242%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcan-create-anarchic-situation-poll-panel-to-m-kharge-on-voter-turnout-data-5632242%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20work%20in%20Norway%2C%20one%20of%20the%20most%20productive%20countries%20in%20the%20world.%20Here's%20why%20%E2%80%93%26nbsp%3Band%20how%20our%20work%20differs%20from%20the%20US.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224608%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Oslo%20Norway%20Harbor%20is%20situated%20on%20the%20Oslo%20Fjord%20in%20Oslo%2C%20Norway.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64dcef794ef9f30019f82419%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222304%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EKenyeres%20Zsolt%2FShutterstock%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ENorway%20is%20often%20in%20the%2010%20happiest%20countries%20in%20the%20world%2C%20but%20is%20also%20in%20the%20top%203%20most%20productive.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EA%20Norwegian%20CEO%20based%20in%20Oslo%20whose%20worked%20in%20the%20US%20shares%20the%20major%20differences.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20said%20Norwegians%20have%20stricter%20boundaries%20between%20work%20and%20home%20life%20and%20are%20never%20late.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20transcribed%20conversation%20with%20Sondre%20Kvam%2C%20co-founder%20and%20CEO%20of%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnaer.io%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ENaer%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%2C%20a%20VR%20platform%20that%20helps%20teams%20improve%20their%20productivity%20with%20fully%20immersive%20workshops%2C%20who%20lives%20in%20Oslo%2C%20Norway.%20The%20conversation%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20live%20and%20work%20in%20Norway%20and%20am%20a%20co-founder%20of%20Naer%2C%20a%20VR%20productivity%20platform.%20I%20work%20with%20employees%20based%20all%20around%20the%20world%20and%20travel%20to%20the%20US%20frequently.%20I%20often%20think%20about%20productivity%20and%20how%20to%20embed%20it%20in%20working%20practices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESweden%20is%20often%20lauded%20for%20its%20working%20practices%2C%20and%20of%20course%2C%20it%20has%20a%20larger%20economy%2C%20but%20it's%20Norway%20that's%20often%20ranked%20as%20one%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fstats.oecd.org%2FIndex.aspx%3FDataSetCode%3DPDB_LV%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emost%20productive%20countries%20in%20the%20world%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Looking%20at%20GDP%20per%20hour%2C%20Norway%20often%20falls%20in%20the%20top%20three%20countries%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.zendesk.co.uk%2Fblog%2Fmost-productive-countries-in-2022%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eglobally%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20aspects%20of%20Norway's%20working%20culture%20contribute%20to%20high%20productivity%20while%20maintaining%20a%20good%20work-life%20balance.%20Norway%20also%20falls%20in%20the%20top%2010%20happiest%20countries%20in%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a0c56b5a-030a-40e0-a9c6-1de20ad55dd3%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EPeople%20spend%20less%20time%20navigating%20workplace%20conflict%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMuch%20of%20our%20work%20life%20is%20based%20around%20the%20Norwegian%20model%20of%20cooperation%20and%20mutual%20respect%20between%20employers%20and%20employees%2C%20unions%2C%20employee%20associations%2C%20and%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20laws%20to%20ensure%20good%20information%20flows%20between%20businesses%20and%20employees.%20For%20instance%2C%20if%20you%20have%20more%20than%2030%20employees%2C%20you're%20obligated%20to%20have%20an%20%26quot%3Bemployee%20representative%26quot%3B%20as%20part%20of%20the%20board.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20unions%20for%20knowledge%20workers%20and%20most%20normal%20jobs%20like%20restaurant%20work.%20Discussions%20between%20unions%20and%20companies%20usually%20happen%20via%20the%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nho.no%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EN%C3%A6ringslivets%20Hovedorganisasjon%26quot%3B%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20NHO%2C%20a%20sort%20of%20union%20businesses%20can%20join.%20Companies%20don't%20have%20to%20join%20the%20NHO%2C%20but%20most%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENorway%20has%20something%20called%20%26quot%3Bl%C3%B8nnsoppgj%C3%B8ret%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3Bthe%20salary%20settlement%26quot%3B%20every%20year%2C%20where%20general%20guidelines%20around%20pay%20are%20established%20for%20each%20industry%20in%20negotiations%20with%20unions%20and%20employer%20associations.%20Once%20a%20wage%20baseline%20has%20been%20set%20in%20each%20sector%2C%20every%20business%20has%20some%20leeway%20to%20give%20more%20to%20high%20performers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECivil%20conversations%20between%20all%20these%20players%20are%20the%20norm%2C%20and%20people%20don't%20spend%20much%20time%20in%20conflicts%20regarding%20workplace%20issues%20because%20they're%20handled%20by%20these%20trusted%20bodies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20of%20that%2C%20Norwegian%20employees%20tend%20to%20be%20focused%20and%20spend%20their%20time%20well%20during%20work%20hours.%20Most%20people%20work%20traditional%20hours%20like%208%20a.m.%20to%204%20p.m.%20or%209%20p.m.%20to%205%20p.m.%20There's%20a%20mentality%20that%20you%20should%20strive%20to%20have%20a%20life%20outside%20work%20by%20working%20set%20hours%20and%20having%20boundaries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228abe3695-47e5-4b4d-9cc5-6db223f0d6a1%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EDeep%20work%20is%20the%20default%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20work%2C%20Norwegians%20are%20working%2C%20and%20deep%20work%20is%20expected%20of%20everyone.%20So%20there's%20no%20doing%20life%20admin%2C%20answering%20LinkedIn%20messages%2C%20chatting%20to%20colleagues%20about%20unrelated%20topics%2C%20or%20online%20shopping%2C%20like%20in%20UK%20or%20US%20offices.%20Most%20of%20the%20time%2C%20Norwegians%20are%20head%20down%20working%20or%20collaborating.%20Pretty%20much%20every%20Norwegian%20has%20some%20sort%20of%20noise-canceling%20headset.%20If%20you're%20wearing%20one%2C%20you%20want%20absolute%20peace.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoing%20to%20the%20US%2C%20I%20often%20hear%20of%20people%20putting%20in%2080-hour%20working%20weeks.%20However%2C%20Americans%20have%20a%20different%20relationship%20to%20the%20workplace%20%E2%80%94%20they%20stay%20later%20because%20they%20have%20longer%20commutes%20and%20maybe%20can%20get%20dinner%2C%20use%20the%20gym%2C%20or%20other%20life%20admin%20services%20at%20their%20offices.%20'Busywork%2C'%20life%20admin%2C%20and%20rest%20time%20all%20happen%20at%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Norway%2C%20anyone%20working%20at%20any%20large%20company%20logs%20off%20and%20continues%20with%20their%20home%20lives%20when%20the%20day's%20allocated%20working%20hours%20are%20up%2C%20which%20are%20tightly%20regulated%20during%20collective%20bargaining.%20That's%20across%20sectors%20%E2%80%94%20banking%2C%20consulting%20firms%2C%20and%20service%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20lot%20of%20people%20turn%20off%20notifications%20outside%20work.%20I've%20set%20up%20my%20notification%20systems%20so%20that%20only%20important%20things%20come%20through%20outside%20work%20hours.%20I%20like%20getting%20up%20early%2C%20reading%20books%2C%20and%20trying%20to%20spend%20time%20with%20things%20relevant%20to%20my%20work.%20There's%20this%20misconception%20that%20being%20constantly%20available%20for%20your%20workplace%20makes%20you%20more%20productive%20or%20faster.%20Being%20constantly%20%26quot%3Bon%26quot%3B%20just%20interrupts%20time%20to%20think%20things%20through%20or%20get%20inspiration%20from%20other%20places.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20an%20understanding%20between%20employers%20and%20employees%20in%20Norway%20that%20you%20will%20do%20better%20work%20if%20you're%20not%20thinking%20about%20work%20all%20the%20time.%20Talking%20of%20work%20outside%20work%20is%20not%20taboo%2C%20but%20you%20don't%20want%20to%20be%20the%20guy%20who%20can't%20shut%20up%20about%20work.%20Norwegians%20are%20encouraged%20to%20take%20holidays%20and%20spend%20time%20with%20their%20families.%20Stress%20and%20exhaustion%20narrow%20your%20perspective%2C%20which%20in%20turn%20degrades%20your%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e821b9d6-531d-4949-94ef-c4ff5efdce88%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAhead%20of%20time%2C%20or%20you're%20late%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Norwegians%2C%20being%20late%20to%20anything%20is%20incredibly%20rude.%20Either%20you're%20ahead%20of%20time%2C%20or%20you're%20late.%20Sitting%20around%20waiting%20for%20someone%20to%20join%20a%20meeting%20is%20one%20of%20the%20things%20Norwegians%20hate%20the%20most.%20It's%20throwing%20both%20money%20and%20time%20out%20of%20the%20window.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20society%2C%20we%20do%20not%20praise%20%26quot%3Bgrinding%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20grinding%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20there's%20an%20awareness%20of%20the%20cost-benefit%20of%20doing%20so.%20I%20don't%20feel%20a%20pressure%20not%20to%20work%2C%20but%20there's%20a%20clear%20expectation%20that%20I%20keep%20an%20eye%20on%20my%20own%20well-being.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20cofounder%20of%20a%20startup%2C%20I%20work%20a%20fair%20amount%2C%20with%20particular%20crunch%20points%20like%20launching%20products%2C%20sorting%20recruitment%2C%20and%20preparing%20for%20a%20fundraise.%20Having%20customers%20in%20other%20time%20zones%20also%20means%20I%20must%20be%20flexible%20with%20my%20work%20schedule%20and%20sometimes%20work%20in%20the%20evening%20or%20early%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20everywhere%20else%2C%20there%20is%20a%20problem%20of%20people%20being%20burned%20out%20as%20founders%20in%20Norway.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20girlfriend%20is%20much%20more%20strict%20on%20the%20boundaries%20of%20her%20work.%20She%20is%20a%20data%20scientist%20and%20backend%20engineer%20for%20a%20Norwegian%20startup.%20When%20she's%20done%20for%20the%20day%2C%20she%20completely%20switches%20messages%20off.%20She%20probably%20gets%20even%20more%20annoyed%20than%20I%20about%20waiting%20for%20someone%20on%20a%20call.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20links%20to%20the%20fact%20we%20have%20limited%20time%20at%20work.%20You%20get%20used%20to%20this%20dynamic%20where%20time%20is%20precious%20and%20hate%20it%20when%20someone's%20late%20outside%20work.%20If%20I%20were%20to%20be%20more%20than%2010%20minutes%20late%20for%20a%20date%20in%20Norway%2C%20that%20would%20be%20unacceptable.%20That%20relationship%20would%20be%20finished%20before%20it%20started%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20a%20total%20dealbreaker.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwork-culture-in-norway-most-productive-country-2024-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715337692000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F663c97fbf27898f532d5531c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwork-culture-in-norway-most-productive-country-2024-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Norway%20often%20ranks%20one%20of%20the%20most%20productive%20countries%20in%20the%20world.%20A%20Norwegian%20CEO%20shares%20why%20the%20work%20culture%20is%20unique.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Megan%20Carnegie)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwork-culture-in-norway-most-productive-country-2024-5%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22My%20mom%20died%20on%20Mother's%20Day%20weekend.%20It's%20a%20painful%20anniversary%2C%20but%20I've%20found%20a%20special%20way%20to%20honor%20her.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222302%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author%20(front)%20with%20her%20sister%2C%20mother%2C%20and%20grandmother%20in%20August%202017%20after%20her%20mom's%20cancer%20diagnosis.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66350ff510dfcda409668dd5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20(front)%20with%20her%20sister%2C%20mother%2C%20and%20grandmother%20in%20August%202017%20after%20her%20mom's%20cancer%20diagnosis.%3Cp%3EPhoto%3A%20Julianne%20Schaer%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMy%20mom%20and%20I%20were%20both%20yoga%20teachers.%20She%20died%20of%20endometrial%20cancer%20just%20before%20Mother's%20Day%202018.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ENow%2C%20on%20Mother's%20Day%20weekend%2C%20I%20teach%20a%20class%20for%20her%20friends%20and%20students.%20It's%20also%20online.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThis%20tradition%20makes%20me%20feel%20connected%20to%20my%20mom%20and%20has%20turned%20my%20pain%20into%20something%20positive.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20people%20hear%20that%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoms-death-taught-me-about-mental-health-in-the-workplace-2022-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Emy%20mom%20died%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20the%20afternoon%20before%20Mother's%20Day%20in%202018%2C%20the%20reaction%20is%20a%20variation%20of%2C%20%26quot%3BOh%2C%20that%20really%20sucks.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYes.%20But%20I've%20found%20a%20way%20to%20turn%20the%20pain%20into%20something%20beautiful.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20anyone%20who%20has%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcaregiver-mother-burned-out-grieving-freedom-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Elost%20a%20mother%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20knows%2C%20Mother's%20Day%20is%20hard%20forever%20after.%20So%20is%20the%20death%20anniversary.%20And%20her%20birthday%2C%20and%20holidays.%20I%20feel%20sad%20every%20February%209%2C%20the%20day%20we%20learned%20my%20mom's%20cancer%20had%20metastasized%2C%20and%20April%2016%2C%20when%20the%20oncologist%20told%20us%20that%20the%20last-ditch%20chemo%20attempt%20had%20failed.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BAt%20least%20we%20kill%20two%20birds%20with%20one%20stone%2C%26quot%3B%20my%20sister%20said%20to%20me%20in%202019.%20Our%20parents%20married%20on%20Mom's%2022nd%20birthday%2C%20so%20we%20get%20another%20two%20tough%20days%20%E2%80%94%20the%20birthday