ew%20Year's%20Day%20where%20she%20guided%20participants%20through%20an%20intention-setting%20process.%20She%20taught%20the%20last%20one%20with%20a%20cap%20over%20her%20bald%20head%20and%20a%20friend%20demonstrating%20the%20poses%20for%20her%20as%20she%20called%20them%20out.%20As%20the%20following%20winter%20holiday%20season%20approached%2C%20the%20owner%20of%20the%20studio%20in%20Hamden%2C%20Connecticut%2C%20asked%20if%20I'd%20help%20continue%20the%20tradition.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221334%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author%20(right)%20with%20her%20mother%20Sue%20Neufeld%20in%202010.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66350bdfec0c69656900d48c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221001%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESara%20Neufeld%20followed%20in%20her%20mom%20Sue's%20steps%20and%20became%20a%20yoga%20teacher.%3Cp%3EPhoto%3A%20Jennifer%20Brosious%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20hesitated.%20My%20yoga%20teaching%20and%20journalism%20careers%20were%20on%20hold%20as%20I%20was%20slammed%20with%20family%20responsibilities%3A%20I%20had%20two%20young%20sons%2C%20and%20after%20my%20mom%20died%2C%20I%20brought%20my%20maternal%20grandmother%20to%20live%20in%20my%20apartment%20building%20in%20Queens.%20(Bubbi%20previously%20lived%20with%20my%20parents.)%20I%20felt%20like%20a%20fraud%20in%20yoga%20as%20I%20struggled%20with%20anxiety%20and%20overwhelm%3B%20I%20was%20just%20figuring%20out%20how%20to%20put%20my%20battered%20postpartum%20body%20back%20together.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20would%20really%20love%20to%20see%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20Jen%2C%20the%20studio%20owner%2C%20said.%20We%20would%20co-teach%2C%20along%20with%20one%20of%20my%20mom's%20friends.%20Nervously%2C%20I%20agreed%2C%20and%20more%20than%2070%20people%20showed%20up.%20I%20asked%20everyone%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhappiness-gratitude-journal-depression-2019-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ewrite%20a%20gratitude%20list%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20and%20specifically%20to%20look%20for%20good%20things%20that%20grew%20out%20of%20pain.%20%26quot%3BLike%20this%20class%2C%26quot%3B%20I%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20experience%20made%20me%20realize%20that%20I%20missed%20teaching%20yoga%2C%20which%20connects%20me%20to%20my%20mom.%20I%20didn't%20want%20to%20wait%20a%20year%20to%20do%20it%20again.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20recalled%20a%20rare%20argument%20that%20my%20mom%20and%20I%20had%20just%20before%20she%20got%20sick.%20She%20wanted%20me%20to%20bring%20my%20kids%2C%20then%20ages%201%20and%203%2C%20to%20her%20house%20in%20Connecticut%20for%20Mother's%20Day.%20My%20husband%20had%20to%20work%2C%20and%20I%20was%20exhausted%20and%20wanted%20her%20to%20come%20to%20me%20in%20New%20York.%20But%20she%20and%20Bubbi%20came%20to%20help%20every%20week.%20%26quot%3BOn%20Mother's%20Day%2C%20you%20come%20to%20Connecticut%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20decided%20to%20teach%20a%20class%20in%20her%20honor%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20listened%20then%20%E2%80%94%20and%20now.%20I%20told%20Jen%20I'd%20teach%20another%20class%20on%20the%20Saturday%20of%20Mother's%20Day%20weekend%2C%20on%20my%20own.%20I%20called%20it%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.yourcommunityyoga.com%2Fwkshp-schedule-list%2F2024%2F5%2F11%2Fremembering-the-divine-mother-wsara-neufeld%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ERemembering%20the%20Divine%20Mother%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20both%20a%20nod%20to%20my%20mom's%20deep%20dive%20into%20yoga's%20spiritual%20aspects%20and%20a%20wish%20for%20participants%20to%20connect%20with%20the%20essence%20of%20motherly%20love%2C%20whether%20or%20not%20they%20ever%20actually%20received%20it.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20time%2C%20nearly%20100%20people%20crammed%20into%20the%20room%2C%20mats%20spilling%20into%20the%20hall.%20My%20mother%20was%20cremated%2C%20but%20if%20she%20had%20a%20grave%2C%20she%20would%20have%20danced%20on%20it%20to%20see%20my%20dad%20and%20Uncle%20Stevie%20doing%20back-to-back%20breathing%20with%20each%20other%2C%20and%20her%20cousin%20Maureen%20practicing%20alongside%20them.%20For%20decades%20she'd%20tried%20to%20interest%20the%20three%20of%20them%20in%20yoga.%20Many%20came%20primarily%20to%20see%20Bubbi%2C%20who%20had%20long%20attended%20my%20mom's%20classes%20and%20at%20age%2092%20participated%20from%20a%20chair.%20I%20did%20my%20best%20to%20accommodate%20everyone%20with%20journaling%2C%20easily%20modifiable%20movement%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fmental-health%2Fhow-to-meditate%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eguided%20relaxation%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20and%20meditation.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20year%20later%2C%20in%20the%20height%20of%20the%20pandemic%2C%20I%20taught%20the%20class%20over%20Zoom%20from%20Bubbi's%20apartment%2C%20upstairs%20from%20my%20own.%20Bubbi%20was%20too%20weak%20to%20do%20the%20movements%20herself%2C%20but%20she%20wrote%20a%20gratitude%20list%20and%20beamed%20with%20pride%20while%20my%20husband%20provided%20tech%20support.%20A%20year%20after%20that%2C%20Bubbi%2C%20too%2C%20had%20died%2C%20and%20I%20taught%20from%20my%20own%20living%20room.%20I%20never%20took%20money%20for%20the%20memorial%20classes%20and%20made%20them%20donation-based%20to%20support%20the%20yoga%20studio.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20packed%20room%20full%20of%20people%20doing%20yoga.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66352a1410dfcda40966a2d9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20first%20Remembering%20the%20Divine%20Mother