0decade%20when%20he%20decided%2C%20at%2038%2C%20to%20pivot%20to%20tech.%20He%20told%20BI%20he%20didn't%20have%20a%20background%20in%20computer%20science%20and%20found%20it%20difficult%20to%20transition%20to%20a%20completely%20new%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPratap%20focused%20on%20networking%20at%20conferences%20for%20engineers%20and%20developers%20and%20inviting%20people%20who%20could%20help%20out%20for%20coffee.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20asking%20questions%20about%20what%20they%20did%20he%20learned%20to%20%26quot%3Bspeak%20to%20engineers%20in%20their%20language%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20he%20told%20BI%20was%20his%20%26quot%3Bbiggest%20advantage.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20started%20working%20at%20a%20small%20software%20development%20company%20and%2C%20after%20a%20year%20and%20a%20half%2C%20landed%20a%20job%20as%20a%20software%20engineer%20at%20Google.%20Before%20landing%20the%20role%2C%20he'd%20been%20rejected%20by%20Google%20four%20times.%20He%20said%20he%20had%20networked%20with%20people%20working%20in%20the%20company%20for%20insight%20into%20how%20things%20there%20worked%20and%20that%20this%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%2C%20to%20land%20the%20role%2C%20he'd%20spent%20time%20speaking%20to%20people%20in%20the%20company%20for%20insight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flanding-job-career-big-tech-interview-amazon-meta-google-apple-2024-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715336676000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F663d067ab4abc992e8c77ee1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flanding-job-career-big-tech-interview-amazon-meta-google-apple-2024-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Five%20people%20who%20landed%20careers%20at%20Big%20Tech%20companies%20share%20exactly%20how%20they%20did%20it.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ehopkins%40insider.com%20(Ella%20Hopkins%2CShubhangi%20Goel)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A13%2