ppening%20in%20India%2C%20a%20change%20is%20needed.%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20has%20the%20blessings%20of%20Lord%20Bajrangbali%2C%20and%20today%20he%20will%20come%20out%20of%20jail.%20I%20think%20it's%20not%20an%20ordinary%20thing.%20He%20is%20coming%20out%20of%20jail%20for%20a%20big%20purpose%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Bharadwarj%2C%20flanked%20by%20AAP%20leaders%20Gopal%20Rai%20and%20Atishi%2C%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AAP%20said%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20order%20is%20essentially%20a%20pushback%20against%20a%20%26quot%3Bconstitutional%20threat%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20parties%20in%20the%20Opposition%20bloc%20INDIA%20have%20long%20been%20accusing%20the%20BJP-led%20central%20government%20of%20using%20central%20agencies%20to%20harass%20rivals%20with%20false%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20out%20of%20jail%2C%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20will%20join%20the%20INDIA%20bloc's%20election%20campaigns%2C%20though%20voting%20in%20three%20of%20the%20seven-phase%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20is%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Bench%20of%20Justices%20Sanjiv%20Khanna%20and%20Dipankar%20Datta%20said%20a%20detailed%20order%20explaining%20why%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20decided%20to%20give%20interim%20bail%20to%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20will%20be%20made%20available%20later%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Thursday%2C%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20(ED)%20had%20opposed%20the%20interim%20relief%20on%20the%20grounds%20that%20a%20politician%20cannot%20claim%20a%20%26quot%3Bspecial%20status%26quot%3B%20higher%20than%20that%20of%20any%20other%20citizen%2C%20and%20is%20as%20much%20liable%20to%20be%20arrested%20and%20detained%20for%20offences%20as%20any%20other%20citizen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20political%20leader%20has%20been%20given%20interim%20bail%20for%20campaigning%2C%20although%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20is%20not%20the%20contesting%20candidate%2C%20the%20ED%20said%20in%20its%20affidavit.%20Even%20a%20contesting%20candidate%20is%20never%20granted%20interim%20bail%20for%20campaigning%20i