rkers%2C%20on%20December%206%2C%20destroyed%20the%20Babri%20Masjid.%20Are%20you%20with%20them%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20are%20allied%20with%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20in%20Delhi...%20the%20same%20AAP%20that%20helped%20BJP%20remove%20Article%20370%20in%20J%26amp%3BK...%20and%20you%20call%20us%20'BJP%20B-team'%3F%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Owaisi%20said%20at%20a%20public%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%202019%20election%20you%20lost%2092%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20seats%20in%20which%20you%20were%20competing%20against%20the%20BJP.%20This%20time%20you%20are%20fighting%20300%20seats...%20tell%20me%2C%20how%20many%20do%20you%20think%20you%20will%20win%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Owaisi's%20sharp%20response%20came%20after%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%2C%20while%20campaigning%20in%20UP's%20Raebareli%2C%20another%20Congress%20bastion%2C%20attacked%20the%20AIMIM%20leader%20for%20working%20with%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20telling%20you%20again%20and%20again.%20Asaduddin%20Owaisi%20is%20working%20directly%20with%20the%20BJP.%20Wherever%20the%20BJP%20needs%20him%20to%20field%20someone%20to%20push%20back%20other%20parties%2C%20he%20is%20doing%20it.%20It%20has%20become%20very%20clear%20in%20Telangana%20elections%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%20May%2013%20election%20for%20Telangana's%2017%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%2C%20including%20the%20Hyderabad%20seat%20that%20has%20been%20held%20by%20Mr%20Owaisi's%20father%20and%20then%20himself%20since%201984%2C%20the%20Congress%20has%20frequently%20accused%20the%20AIMIM%20of%20being%20the%20BJP's%20'B-team'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20charge%20was%20firmly%20rubbished%20by%20Mr%20Owaisi's%20brother%2C%20Akbaruddin%20Owaisi%2C%20last%20month.%20%26quot%3BSome%20are%20saying%20AIMIM%20is%20with%20that%20team%2C%20some%20are%20saying%20it%20is%20with%20the%20other%20team.%20But%20what%20I%20am%20saying%20is%20that%20AIMIM%20will%20be%20w