.%20They%20include%20asexual%20individuals%2C%20homosexuals%2C%20and%20heterosexuals%20who%20are%20disillusioned%20with%20traditional%20marriage.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20agency%20called%20Colorus%2C%20which%20specialises%20in%20friendship%20marriage%2C%20shared%20the%20data%20related%20to%20this%20new%20trend.%20According%20to%20its%20data%2C%20since%20March%202015%2C%20around%20500%C2%A0people%20in%20Japan%20have%20indulged%20in%20this%20type%20of%20marriage.%20They%20have%20formed%20households%20and%20some%20have%20even%20raised%20children%2C%20the%20agency%20revealed%2C%20per%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scmp.com%2Fnews%2Fpeople-culture%2Fgender-diversity%2Farticle%2F3260278%2Fwhat-friendship-marriage-pals-platonic-partners-japanese-couples-embrace-unions-without-romance-or%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESCMP%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20friendship%20marriage%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFriendship%20marriage%20is%20a%20type%20of%20relationship%20where%20partners%20are%20legally%20spouses%20but%20without%20romantic%20love%20or%20sexual%20interaction.%20They%20can%20live%20together%20or%20separately.%20Couples%20can%20also%20decide%20to%20have%20children%20through%20artificial%20insemination.%20In%20this%20relationship%2C%20both%20individuals%20are%20also%20free%20to%20pursue%20romantic%20relationships%20with%20other%20people%20outside%20the%20marriage%2C%20as%20long%20as%20there%20is%20a%20mutual%20agreement.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFriendship%20marriage%20is%20like%20finding%20a%20roommate%20with%20similar%20interests%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20an%20individual%20who%20has%20been%20in%20such%20an%20arrangement%20for%20three%20years%2C%20per%20%3Cem%3ESCMP%3C%2Fem%3E.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20not%20suited%20to%20be%20someone's%20girlfriend%2C%20but%20I%20can%20be%20a%20good%20friend.%20I%20only%20wanted%20someone%20with%20similar%20tastes%20to%20do%20things%20we%20both%20enjoy%2C%20to%20chat%20and%20laugh%20with%2C%26quot%3B%20another%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20does%20friendship%20marriage%20work%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20arrangement%20is%20not%20about%20traditional%20romantic%20love%20or%20marrying%20a%20best%20friend.%20Instead%2C%20under%20this%20arrangement%2C%20couples%20usually%20meet%20before%20marriage%20and%20spend%20hours%20or%20days%20agreeing%20on%20the%20details%20of%20their%20life%2C%20such%20as%20whether%20to%20eat%20meals%20together%2C%20how%20to%20split%20expenses%2C%20who%20does%20the%20laundry%20and%20how%20to%20allocate%20refrigerator%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20seeming%20unromantic%2C%20such%20discussions%20have%20helped%20nearly%2080%25%20of%20couples%20in%20this%20relationship%20type%20to%20live%20together%20happily%2C%20Colorus%20said.%20The%20agency%20added%20that%20in%20many%20cases%2C%20some%20couples%20even%20have%20children%20together.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20is%20choosing%20friendship%20marriage%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Cem%3ESCMP%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20people%20interested%20in%20this%20type%20of%20relationship%20are%20on%20average%2032.5%20years%20old%20with%20incomes%20exceeding%20the%20national%20average.%20This%20trend%20is%20also%20gaining%20traction%20among%20asexual%20individuals%20and%20homosexuals%20trying%20to%20avoid%20traditional%20marriage%20patterns.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20some%20homosexuals%2C%20who%20dislike%20traditional%20marriage%20patterns%20or%20romantic%20relationships%20but%20are%20subject%20to%20societal%20pressures%2C%20have%20also%20been%20embracing%20this%20new%20trend%2C%20the%20outlet%20reported.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20these%20types%20of%20relationships%20sometimes%20end%20in%20divorce%2C%20the%20advantages%20include%20enjoying%20policy%20benefits%2C%20companionship%20and%20%26quot%3Bhelping%20those%20who%20feel%20lost%2C%20dislike%20traditional%20marriage%2C%20or%20consider%20themselves%20social%20outcasts%26quot%3B%2C%20Colorus%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715325300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fc39fdicg_couple-generic_625x300_10_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Ffriendship-marriage-all-about-japans-new-relationship-trend-that-excludes-love-or-sex-5630866%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20new%20relationship%20trend%20called%20%26quot%3Bfriendship%20marriage%26quot%3B%20is%20gaining%20popularity%20among%20young%20people%20in%20Japan.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Ffriendship-marriage-all-about-japans-new-relationship-trend-that-excludes-love-or-sex-5630866%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Ffriendship-marriage-all-about-japans-new-relationship-trend-that-excludes-love-or-sex-5630866%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Ffriendship-marriage-all-about-japans-new-relationship-trend-that-excludes-love-or-sex-5630866%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22S%20Jaishankar%20Warns%20Of%20Global%20Geopolitical%20%26quot%3BStorm%26quot%3B%2C%20Outlines%20India's%20Role%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20world%20will%20witness%20a%20%26quot%3Bvery%2C%20very%20stormy%26quot%3B%20churn%20because%20of%20conflicts%2C%20power%20shifts%20and%20sharpening%20competition%20in%20this%20decade%2C%20which%20makes%20it%20all%20the%20more%20important%20for%20India%20to%20have%20a%20stable%20and%20mature%20leadership%2C%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%20S%20Jaishankar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20exclusive%20interview%20to%20Press%20Trust%20of%20India%2C%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20painted%20a%20picture%20of%20the%20world%20radically%20different%20from%20the%20one%20we%20are%20living%20in%20now%20by%20the%20end%20of%202020s%20when%20asked%20to%20draw%20on%20his%20nearly%2050%20years%20of%20experience%20in%20diplomacy%20and%20politics%20to%20give%20an%20assessment%20of%20the%20global%20power%20balance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMultiple%20conflicts%2C%20tensions%2C%20divides!%20With%20all%20these%20variables%20that%20I%20am%20putting%20to%20you%2C%20I%20am%20painting%20to%20you%2C%20actually%2C%20a%20very%2C%20very%20stormy%20international%20scene%20for%20the%20balance%20of%20the%20decade%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Jaishankar%2C%20a%20former%20ambassador%20to%20China%20and%20the%20United%20States%2C%20who%20was%20tapped%20for%20the%20political%20role%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Jaishankar%20especially%20referred%20to%20the%20declining%20influence%20of%20the%20United%20States%2C%20the%20conflict%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20the%20fighting%20in%20Gaza%2C%20attacks%20in%20the%20Red%20Sea%2C%20tensions%20in%20the%20South%20China%20Sea%2C%20the%20challenge%20of%20terrorism%20in%20different%20geographies%20and%20advent%20of%20new%20technologies%20as%20the%20drivers%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Bchurn%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20the%20combination%20of%20all%20of%20this%20today%2C%20poses%20a%20kind%20of%20a%20picture%20of%20great%20churn%2C%20and%20on%20top%20of%20it%20the%20competition%20is%20sharpening%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20context%2C%20he%20added%20it%20is%20imperative%20that%20voters%20in%20the%20ongoing%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20choose%20wisely%20so%20India%20continues%20to%20have%20a%20stable%20and%20mature%20leadership.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20today%2C%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20choices%20which%20the%20Indian%20voters%20have%20to%20make%20is%20in%20this%20situation%20--%20whom%20do%20you%20trust%20to%20lead%20the%20Indian%20government%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20pitching%20for%20continuation%20of%20the%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Jaishankar%2C%20who%20has%20a%20massive%20following%20in%2