nd%20its%20southern%20stronghold%20of%20Karnataka%2C%20the%20BJP%20secured%20an%20impressive%20four%20out%20of%20the%20total%2017%20seats%20in%20Telangana%20in%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%20This%20was%20achieved%20by%20finishing%20as%20a%20runner-up%20and%20limiting%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fanother-blow-to-kcr-chevella-mp-ranjith-reddy-quits-brs-over-current-political-circumstances-ahead-of-2024-lok-sabha-elections-5255406%5C%22%3Eregional%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samithi%3C%2Fa%3E%20(BRS%2C%20formerly%20Telangana%20Rashtra%20Samiti)%20to%20a%20single-digit%20tally%2C%20thus%20limiting%20the%20party's%20grip%20on%20the%20state%20since%20the%20formation%20of%20Telangana%20in%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20setback%20in%20the%20December%202023%20assembly%20elections%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20re-emerged%20as%20the%20principal%20challenger%20to%20the%20Congress%20party%2C%20which%20secured%20the%20mandate%20to%20govern%20the%20state%20under%20the%20leadership%20of%20Chief%20Minister%20Revanth%20Reddy.%20Conversely%2C%20after%20facing%20rejection%20by%20the%20people%20and%20concluding%20a%20decade-long%20tenure%20in%20office%2C%20the%20BRS%20and%20its%20leader%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fvideo%2Fnews%2Fnews%2Fkcr-barred-from-campaigning-for-derogatory-remarks-against-congress-780598%5C%22%3EK.%20Chandrashekar%20Rao%20(KCR)%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20are%20hoping%20to%20regain%20some%20of%20their%20lost%20prestige%20in%20Telangana.%20Effectively%2C%20the%20contest%20for%20the%2017%20seats%20should%20be%20seen%20as%20triangular%2C%20though%20with%20few%20exceptions%20-%20especially%20the%20high-profile%20Hyderabad%20constituency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EAdvantage%20Incumbency%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERevanth%20Reddy%2C%20who%20led%20the%20Congress%20party%20to%20victory%20in%20the%20December%20assembly%20elections%2C%20faces%20the%20test%20of%20delivering%20and%20raising%20his%20party's%20Lok%20Sabha%20tally%20in%20the%20state%20from%20the%20current%20three.%20The%20Congress%20campaign%20spotlight%20is%20on%20the%20party's%20commitment%20to%20implementing%20the%20five%20guarantees.%20Despite%20financial%20constraints%2C%20the%20state%20government%20has%20managed%20to%20fulfil%20four%20of%20the%20six%20guarantees%20it%20promised.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20schemes%20that%20have%20gained%20traction%20is%20the%20free%20bus%20ride%20programme%20for%20women.%20According%20to%20official%20estimates%2C%20approximately%2030%20lakh%20beneficiaries%20avail%20of%20this%20facility%20every%20month%2C%20resulting%20in%20an%20estimated%20saving%20of%20Rs%201%2C150%20crore%20for%20women%20since%20the%20scheme's%20implementation%20in%20December.%20The%20free%20bus%20travel%20experience%20may%20also%20be%20expanded%20with%20the%20Indian%20National%20Congress%20promising%20'Nari%20Nyay'%2C%20under%20which%20it%20will%20provide%20Rs%201%20Lakh%20annually%20for%20women%20belonging%20to%20poorer%20sections.%20There%20are%20four%20other%20promises%20on%20offer%3A%20Rs%201%20lakh%20for%20educated%20youth%20through%20employment%20opportunities%2C%20loan%20waiver%20for%20farmers%2C%20Rs%20400%20per%20day%20minimum%20wage%2C%20and%20a%20caste%20census%20for%20better%20targeting%20of%20welfare%20schemes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fin-telangana-kcrs-leaders-swell-congress-bjp-ranks-ahead-of-polls-5361708%5C%22%3ERead%20%7C%C2%A0In%20Telangana%2C%20KCR's%20Leaders%20Swell%20Congress%2C%20BJP%20Ranks%20Ahead%20of%20Polls%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20limiting%20itself%20to%20mere%20delivery%20and%20promises%2C%20the%20Congress%20has%20also%20not%20shied%20away%20from%20fielding%20candidates%20who%20defected%20from%20other%20parties.%20Among%20them%20are%20Ranjit%20Reddy%2C%20Danam%20Nagender%2C%20and%20P.%20Dayakar%2C%20all%20of%20whom%20underwent%20a%20%3Cem%3EGhar%20Wapasi%20%3C%2Fem%3E(homecoming).%20Conversely%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20imported%20candidates%20from%20the%20BRS.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EBJP's%20Strategy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20loss%20of%20momentum%20it%20witnessed%20during%20the%20assembly%20polls%20under%20its%20former%20state%20chief%20Bandi%20Sanjay%2C%20the%20BJP%20is%20now%20striving%20to%20bolster%20its%20national%20campaign%20to%20make%20way%20for%20a%20third%20term%20for%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%20Unlike%20in%202014%2C%20when%20the%20state%20voted%20as%20a%20single%20entity%20and%20gave%20a%20majority%20of%20the%20nine%20seats%20to%20the%20BRS%2C%20the%20BJP's%20objective%20now%20is%20to%20secure%20seats%20in%20double%20digits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20concerted%20effort%20to%20build%20on%20its%20nearly%2020%25%20vote%20share%20in%202019%20has%20seen%20the%20BJP%20leadership%2C%20including%20PM%20Modi%20and%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20dedicating%20time%20to%20campaign%20for%20party%20candidates.%20In%20addition%20to%20emphasising%20issues%20such%20as%20the%20Congress's%20alleged%20favouring%20of%20minorities%20at%20the%20expense%20of%20others%2C%20campaigners%20are%20out%20to%20confront%20the%20perception%20that%20the%20%3Cem%3EAbki%20Baar%20400-paar%3C%2Fem%3E%20slogan%20signifies%20an%20intention%20to%20alter%20the%20Constitution%20and%20abolish%20reservations%20for%20Scheduled%20Castes%2FTribes.%20As%20a%20rebuttal%2C%20the%20campaign%20is%20focusing%20on%20'%3Cem%3EModi%20ki%20Guarantee%3C%2Fem%3E'%20(Modi's%20guarantee)%2C%20highlighting%20how%20welfare%20schemes%20have%20benefited%20all%20without%20discrimination.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EBRS's%20Challenges%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20former%20chief%20minister%20KCR%2C%20who%20was%20a%20staunch%20advocate%20of%20a%20separate%20state%2C%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20present%20an%20opportunity%20to%20remind%20the%20people%20of%20his%20contributions.%20In%20addition%20to%20his%2