0%20small%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F256110%2Fanand-dhawaj-negi-himachal-pradesh-forest-cold-desert-thang-karma-kinnaur-district-environment-conservation-tree-plantation-apricot-apple-nor41%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eapple%20farmers%20%3C%2Fa%3Eof%20Kinnaur.%20Today%2C%20he%20runs%20a%20startup%20%E2%80%98Kayang%E2%80%99%20to%20supply%20Kinnauri%20apples%20to%20customers%20directly%20%E2%80%94%20saving%20them%20from%20a%20vicious%20circle%20of%20middlemen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHomecoming%20and%20the%20moment%20of%20truth%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20coming%20back%20to%20his%20village%2C%20the%20first%20thing%20Ashish%20did%20was%20to%20learn%20how%20to%20become%20a%20farmer%20before%20entering%20into%20the%20apple%20business.%20He%20picked%20up%20a%20shovel%20and%20started%20working%20on%20the%20apple%20orchard%2C%20which%20he%20says%20was%20not%20in%20great%20shape.%20It%20took%20him%20three%20to%20four%20years%20to%20make%20the%2015-%3Cem%3Ebigha%3C%2Fem%3E%20farmland%20cultivable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20he%20owns%20the%201%2C500%20apple%20trees%20in%20his%20orchard%20and%20also%20grows%20other%20crops%20%E2%80%94%20including%20wild%20apricots%2C%20pulses%2C%20%3Cem%3Erajma%3C%2Fem%3E%20(red%20kidney%20bean)%2C%20seasonal%20vegetables%2C%20and%20buckwheat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20he%20went%20to%20the%20local%20market%20to%20sell%20his%20produce%2C%20he%20observed%20that%20the%20tribal%20growers%20were%20at%20the%20mercy%20of%20middlemen.%20Sharing%20his%20first-hand%20experience%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20whole%20market%20system%20was%20totally%20corrupt%2C%20biased%2C%20and%20against%20farmers.%20It%20favoured%20big%20firms%2C%20companies%2C%20and%20middlemen.%20At%20least%20five%20distributors%20are%20involved%20before%20the%20apples%20reach%20from%20the%20grower%20to%20the%20consumer.%20These%20people%20benefit%20more%20than%20the%20grower.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FKinnaur-apples-1-1-1715174359.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Among%20the%20popular%20varieties%20grown%20in%20Kinnaur%2C%20their%20Royal%20%E2%80%98Black%20Gold%E2%80%99%20apples%20have%20a%20huge%20demand%20among%20buyers.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FKinnaur-apples-1-1-1715174359.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FKinnaur-apples-1-1-1715174359-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FKinnaur-apples-1-1-1715174359-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FKinnaur-apples-1-1-1715174359-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FKinnaur-apples-1-1-1715174359-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-349338%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAmong%20the%20popular%20varieties%20grown%20in%20Kinnaur%2C%20their%20Royal%20%E2%80%98Black%20Gold%E2%80%99%20apples%20have%20a%20huge%20demand%20among%20buyers.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAshish%20adds%20that%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F261819%2Ffarmer-how-to-grow-himachal-apples-wine-capital-of-india-nashik-organic%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20Kinnauri%20apples%20%3C%2Fa%3Eare%20one%20of%20the%20most%20expensive%20ones%20in%20the%20world%2C%20and%20yet%2C%20the%20apple%20growers%20never%20receive%20their%20fair%20share.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20would%20get%20payment%20almost%2015%20to%2020%20days%20late%20or%20somet