e-349341%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAshish%20became%20a%20saviour%20to%20at%20least%201%2C000%20small%20apple%20farmers%20of%20Kinnaur.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20popular%20varieties%20grown%20in%20the%20region%2C%20their%20Royal%20%E2%80%98Black%20Gold%E2%80%99%20apples%20have%20a%20huge%20demand%20among%20buyers.%20%E2%80%9CCompared%20to%20the%20reddish-coloured%20apples%2C%20these%20are%20darker%20in%20colour%20and%20one%20of%20the%20costliest%20apples%20worldwide.%20That%E2%80%99s%20how%20it%20gets%20its%20name%2C%20Black%20Gold.%20Its%20taste%2C%20crunchiness%2C%20and%20juiciness%20add%20to%20its%20uniqueness.%20That%E2%80%99s%20why%20it%20has%20a%20high%20value.%20And%20these%20can%20be%20grown%20only%20in%20our%20region%20given%20our%20climatic%20conditions%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20year%2C%20Ashish%20aims%20to%20commercialise%20value-added%20products%20of%20these%20apples%20to%20further%20the%20income%20of%20regional%20farmers.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20aim%20to%20process%20apples%20into%20jams%2C%20vinegar%2C%20juices%2C%20and%20healthy%20dried%20apple%20chips.%20Our%20processing%20unit%20will%20be%20operational%20from%20September%20onwards%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20reveals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELooking%20back%20at%20his%20city%20life%2C%20Ashish%20finds%20contentment%20in%20rural%20farm%20life.%20%E2%80%9CI%20enjoy%20my%20field%20of%20work%20as%20I%20get%20to%20meet%20real%20India%20%E2%80%93%20its%20small%20farmers.%20With%20my%20work%2C%20I%20see%20improvements%20in%20front%20of%20me%20every%20day.%20These%20farmers%20were%20once%20in%20distress%20and%20at%20the%20mercy%20of%20middlemen.%20To%20be%20able%20to%20help%20them%20even%20on%20a%20very%20basic%20level%20is%20so%20fulfilling.%20We%20are%20not%20just%20helping%20a%20person%2C%20we%E2%80%99re%20helping%20the%20whole%20family%20and%20the%20community%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%