ab%20explains%2C%20nothing%20is%20voluntary.%20The%20doctors%20and%20all%20medical%20technicians%20appointed%20for%20the%20boats%20are%20paid%20a%20salary.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20to%20ensure%20that%20it%20is%20a%20continuation%20of%20service%20and%20the%20patients%20will%20not%20be%20stranded.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20heartwarming%20to%20watch%20a%20community%20that%20was%20once%20starved%20of%20medical%20attention%20now%20on%20the%20path%20to%20better%20healthcare%20services.%20But%20bringing%20about%20this%20radical%20change%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20been%20a%20day%E2%80%99s%20job%2C%20notes%20Wohab%2C%20as%20he%20dives%20into%20the%20setting%20up%20of%20the%20SHIS%20Foundation%2C%20and%20how%20he%20and%20Pal%20transcended%20the%20obstacles%20that%20showed%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EInvesting%20resources%3A%20both%20financial%20and%20emotional%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpread%20across%201%2C40%2C000%20hectares%20at%20the%20confluence%20of%20the%20deltas%20of%20the%20Ganges%2C%20Brahmaputra%20and%20Meghna%20rivers%2C%20the%20Sundarban%20mangrove%20forest%20sees%20a%20heavy%20intersection%20of%20tidal%20waterways%20and%20islands.%20While%20this%20is%20a%20picture%20of%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F336784%2Fifs-officer-jagdish-bakan-wins-unesco-award-gulf-of-mannar-biosphere-reserve%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eperfect%20ecosystem%3C%2Fa%3E%20it%20also%20means%20tough%20commuting%20for%20the%20locals.%20The%20people%20of%20the%20delta%20must%20walk%20for%20hours%20to%20avail%20of%20any%20facility.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fmatheran--1714725403.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Through%20SHIS%20Foundation%20there%20are%20medi