ol%20strategy%20recommended%20by%20the%20World%20Health%20Organisation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20its%20clinics%20and%20volunteer%20base%2C%20SHIS%20is%20attempting%20to%20help%20hinder%20the%20progression%20of%20tuberculosis%20right%20at%20the%20onset.%20Wohab%20shares%20that%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F337918%2Fbengaluru-sanathya-foundation-provides-free-wheelchair-nebulizer-medical-equipment-on-rent%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20programme%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20one%20of%20their%20biggest%20chapters%20aside%20from%20the%20boat%20clinics.%20%E2%80%9CMore%20than%2040%2C000%20people%20have%20been%20able%20to%20manage%20their%20TB%20through%20the%20medicines%20that%20we%20provide%20them.%E2%80%9D%20He%20adds%20that%20they%20procure%20these%20medicines%20from%20the%20Government%20for%20free.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fshis-1-1714725680.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20community%20delivery%20centres%20ensure%20that%20women%20have%20a%20safe%20environment%20where%20they%20can%20give%20birth%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fshis-1-1714725680.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fshis-1-1714725680-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fshis-1-1714725680-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fshis-1-1714725680-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fshis-1-1714725680-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-348891%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%