nkush%20wanted%20to%20appear%20on%20Shark%20Tank%20India.%20Even%20though%20he%20could%20not%20make%20it%20to%20season%202%2C%20he%20made%20a%20lasting%20impression%20on%20the%20%E2%80%98sharks%E2%80%99%20in%20season%203.%20The%20impact%20of%20the%20episode%20was%20so%20enormous%20that%20he%20observed%20a%20boost%20of%20six%20times%20in%20his%20business%2C%20he%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERooted%20in%20his%20village%2C%20Ankush%20now%20aims%20to%20make%20a%20business%20of%20Rs%20150%20crore%2C%20enter%20into%20export%20in%20at%20least%2010%20countries%2C%20and%20open%20offline%20stores%20in%20the%20next%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20do%20not%20feel%20I%20have%20achieved%20very%20big.%20It%20was%20through%20my%20grandfather%E2%80%99s%20efforts%20that%20we%20started%20getting%20meals%20three%20times%20a%20day.%20My%20parents%20worked%20hard%20so%20that%20we%20could%20wear%20decent%20clothes.%20I%20just%20want%20to%20give%20whatever%20best%20life%20I%20can%20to%20my%20parents%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CRecently%2C%20I%20gifted%20a%20seven-seater%20car%20to%20my%20father.%20Currently%2C%20we%20are%20building%20our%20dream%20house%20with%20a%20helipad%20and%20rooftop%20swimming%20pool%20in%20Himachal%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CAlthough%20these%20are%20materialistic%20things%2C%20having%20a%20%3Cem%3Ebada%20ghar%2C%20badi%20gaadi%20%3C%2Fem%3E(big%20house%2C%20big%20car)%20are%20dreams%20of%20a%20lower-middle%20income%20family.%20In%20eight%20months%2C%20I%20will%20move%20to%20our%20new%20home%20with%20my%20family.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat.%20All%20photos%3A%20Ankush%20Barjata.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714745043000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FAnkush-1714728877.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D348898%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ankush%20Barjata%20founded%20an%20online