%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Epuri%20bhajiya%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3C%2Fa%3E(a%20fast%20food%20stall)%20stall%20in%20Siliguri%2C%20West%20Bengal.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20he%20came%20to%20live%20at%20our%20centre%20for%20his%20child%E2%80%99s%20treatment%20(which%20lasted%20six%20months)%2C%20he%20had%20to%20sell%20his%20cart%20back%20home.%20He%20was%20worried%20about%20what%20would%20happen%20to%20his%20livelihood.%20But%20during%20his%20time%20here%2C%20he%20learnt%20how%20to%20make%20%3Cem%3Evada%20pav%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20started%20selling!%20The%20business%20was%20a%20huge%20success%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGirish%20pitches%20in%20with%20another%20heartwarming%20story.%20%E2%80%9COne%20of%20the%20parents%20was%20a%20soldier%20who%20quit%20and%20came%20to%20our%20Mumbai%20centre%20when%20his%20child%20was%20admitted.%20But%20in%20the%20weeks%20that%20followed%2C%20he%20saw%20how%20well%20his%20son%20was%20being%20cared%20for%20at%20the%20centre.%20That%20enabled%20him%20to%20go%20back%20to%20his%20duty%20peacefully.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20duo%20encourages%20both%20parents%20to%20stay%20with%20the%20child%20at%20the%20centre%2C%20they%20are%20aware%20that%20this%20is%20not%20always%20possible%20and%20are%20always%20willing%20to%20make%20exceptions.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20there%20is%20a%20family%20that%20has%20two%20kids%20and%20one%20is%20admitted%20here%20and%20the%20other%20is%20an%20infant%2C%20we%20ask%20the%20family%20to%20bring%20both%20kids%20so%20they%20can%20all%20live%20here%2C%E2%80%9D%20Girish%20shares.%20They%20go%20to%20great%20lengths%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20comfort%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F327071%2Fvaranasi-ias-officer-himanshu-nagpal-mission-muskaan-reunites-lost-children-with-families%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20families%3C%2Fa%3E%20trumps%20everything%20else.%C2%A0%3C%2F